<li class='cover' id='bookCover_13542833'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13542833-the-shortest-way-home"><img alt="The Shortest Way Home" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348197304l/13542833._SX98_.jpg" />
