<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer2205482522343046692"> Robert Hicks has been active in the music industry in Nashville for twenty years as both a music publisher and artist manager. The driving force behind the perservation and restoration of the historic Carnton plantation in Tennessee, he stumbled upon the extraordinary role that Carrie McGavock played during and after the Battle of Franklin. He is the author of <i>The Widow of the South</i> and <i>A Separat</i></span>
  <span id="freeText2205482522343046692" style="display:none"> Robert Hicks has been active in the music industry in Nashville for twenty years as both a music publisher and artist manager. The driving force behind the perservation and restoration of the historic Carnton plantation in Tennessee, he stumbled upon the extraordinary role that Carrie McGavock played during and after the Battle of Franklin. He is the author of <i>The Widow of the South</i> and <i>A Separate Country</i>.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2205482522343046692" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

